entries.femaleVariant: Jackster. Talked to Dex.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Gordito" b="Heheh. " a="'s a big deal – literally and not, yeah?"/>
So, uh, Militech – what'd you decide?
We met, we chatted. It was nice. May be somethin' there, maybe not.
Guy certainly knows how to protect his biz. Wants to put us on a few small kinks, prep work, I guess, before linin' us up a big job.
He was out to work me over.
Claimed to want to check our pro cred. But to me it feels more like he tangled us up with Maelstrom and Militech.
Wants to check us out, see if we got what it takes.
OK. Whatcha waitin' for? Gimme the detes.
Agh, don't thrill you, that?
Feels like a fuckin' test. Talks about believin' in us, but then asks us to prove our worth? I dunno.
There's this combat bot, military prototype? Maelstrom klepped it. Then Dex paid to take it off their hands just before the gangoons had a switch-up in management.
entries.maleVariant: There's this combat bot, military prototype. Maelstrom klepped it. Then Dex paid to take it off their hands just before the gangoons had a switch-up in management.

Visit Maelstrom first.

I say we knock on Maelstrom's door first. Pound, actually.
Parker – think I oughta see her first. See what she's like, what she's after.
Meet you there once I'm done.
'Ey, oh, V – just one more thing…
<kiroshi l="mex" o="V. Háblame." t="V. Talk to me." b="" a=""/>
Met the client. Her name's Parker. Evelyn Parker.
We agreed to have a face-to-face. So we'll see.
Hey V... just keep an eye out, OK?
Waitin' for ya at All Foods, ya know. Not gettin' any younger.
Nothin' yet.
'Ey, I wouldn't league up with Militech if I was you. They don't cut deals, they cut throats. Anyway…
Yeah?
'Bout sums it up. Dex wants us talkin' to Royce. Gave the detes of some Militech agent, too, but... dunno how much help she stands to be.

Got friends in high places.
Uhh, she's got friends in high places... clouds, like.

entries.femaleVariant: Odd. Somethin's off about her.
Something's off about her, don't know what.
Uh-huh. Like what?

We-he-ll, so do we. We workin' with Dex, now.
Parker knows Yorinobu Arasaka. They fuck.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="¡Mierda!" b="" a=" Oh fuck!"/>
Yo, got a good nose for shady shit, V, you know that. An' I say keep those corpos sidelined.
Militech – what'd you decide?
What'd you decide to do about Militech?
Ah, good. My vote's to keep it that way, right?
<kiroshi l="mex" o="Hasta luego." t="See ya later." b="" a=""/>
Hm? Who is she? What's she like?
Right, right, heard about that. Royce versus Brick – hostile takeover.
Then there's the other thing.
Then there's the other thing. Gotta meet the client who put the job on the table – Evelyn Parker.
Ick, you don't sound thrilled. Royce – whaddaya know about him?
Royce – know anything about him?
There's psychopaths... and there's psychopaths. Know what I mean?
He's fuckin' whacked somethin' special. Junkies snort junk, Royce snorts chrome.
You? Well, what's Dex gonna do – ride around in his limo, chat chicks up on the holo?
Parker wants to meet someone on the crew. Dex gave me the nod.
Must know what he's doin'… So, how you wanna play this? Maelstrom or Parker, what's first?
